rt</p></div><div btn-arrow=\"right\" class=\"arrow is-button\"><div class=\"icon-embed-xsmall w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M5 13h11.17l-4.88 4.88c-.39.39-.39 1.03 0 1.42s1.02.39 1.41 0l6.59-6.59a.996.996 0 0 0 0-1.41l-6.58-6.6a.996.996 0 1 0-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H5c-.55 0-1 .45-1 1s.45 1 1 1\"></path></svg></div></div></a></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"divider-horizontal\"></div><div class=\"impact-header_component\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_component\"><div class=\"padding-section-xsmall\"><div data-wf--breadcrumb-original--variant=\"base\" class=\"breadcrumb_component\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_div\"><a href=\"/careers\" class=\"breadcrumb_link w-inline-block\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_page\">Careers</div></a><div class=\"breadcrumb_icon w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M5 13h11.17l-4.88 4.88c-.39.39-.39 1.03 0 1.42s1.02.39 1.41 0l6.59-6.59a.996.996 0 0 0 0-1.41l-6.58-6.6a.996.996 0 1 0-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H5c-.55 0-1 .45-1 1s.45 1 1 1\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"breadcrumb_div\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_current-page\">Work experience</div></div></div></div></div><div grow-scroll=\"reverse\" class=\"impact-header_image-wrapper is-radius\"><img data-scroll=\"\" data-scroll-speed=\"-0.05\" alt=\"Three adults sitting at a wooden table writing notes with pens on notebooks or paper.\" loading=\"eager\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69f1ca86d1d79fea7a5bc501_meeting_under_1mb.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1501px) 100vw, 1501px\" srcset=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69f1ca86d1d79fea7a5bc501_meeting_under_1mb-p-500.jpg 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69f1ca86d1d79fea7a5bc501_meeting_under_1mb-p-800.jpg 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69f1ca86d1d79fea7a5bc501_meeting_under_1mb-p-1080.jpg 1080w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69f1ca86d1d79fea7a5bc501_meeting_under_1mb-p-1600.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69f1ca86d1d79fea7a5bc501_meeting_under_1mb-p-2000.jpg 2000w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69f1ca86d1d79fea7a5bc501_meeting_under_1mb.jpg 2048w\" class=\"impact-header_image\"></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"listing_shape-wrapper\"><div lottie=\"target-load\" class=\"header_shape is-impact\" data-w-id=\"b44880a4-d96e-f7f4-464a-54228d5b2be7\" data-animation-type=\"lottie\" data-src=\"/assets/69db9824440585a4bf466988_V_Yellow.json\" data-loop=\"0\" data-direction=\"1\" data-autoplay=\"1\" data-is-ix2-target=\"0\" data-renderer=\"svg\" data-default-duration=\"0\" data-duration=\"3\" data-loading=\"lazy\"></div></div></header><header class=\"section_team-profile-large_header-1\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"team-profile-large_header-1_component\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid team-profile-large_header-1_content\"><div class=\"team-profile-large_header-1_content-left\"><h2>What to expect during your placement</h2></div><div class=\"team-profile-large_header-1_content-right\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><p>‍</p><p>Our week long placements give you a real feel for life at a busy, modern law firm. Whether you’re just starting to explore a legal career or already working towards qualification, it’s a chance to grow your confidence, pick up practical skills, and learn directly from experienced professionals.</p><p>‍</p><p>You’ll get stuck into real legal work from the start. That means helping with research, joining client meetings, and getting to grips with live cases. You’ll meet people across the firm, hear their stories, and learn about the different routes into law. You’ll also be welcome at any events happening during your week. Most importantly, you’ll be treated like one of the team from day one.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></header><header class=\"section_team-profile-large_header-1\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"team-profile-large_header-1_component\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid team-profile-large_header-1_content\"><div class=\"team-profile-large_header-1_content-left\"><h2>How to apply</h2></div><div class=\"team-profile-large_header-1_content-right\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><p>If you’d like to apply for the Scheme, please email your CV and a covering letter to our Work Experience Coordinators, Maariyah ShaUgandaat and Zaiwara Mehran. Please make sure your letter includes all the information listed below.</p><ul role=\"list\"><li>Let us know whether you’re currently at school, college, university or in work and tell us a bit about what you’re doing.</li><li>Share the results from your most recent exams.</li><li>Tell us why you’d like to do your work experience placement with us.</li><li>Let us know what you think you’ll bring to the team during your time with us.</li><li>What achievement are you most proud of?</li><li>Tell us when you’re available for your placement.</li></ul><p><a href=\"https://university.webflow.com/lesson/add-and-nest-text-links-in-webflow\">All placements take place in our Kampala office. We get a high volume of applications and can only consider those that meet all of the above criteria.<br><em>‍</em></a></p><p><a href=\"https://university.webflow.com/lesson/add-and-nest-text-links-in-webflow\"><em>*APPLICATIONS ARE FULL UNTIL SEPTEMBER 2026</em></a></p><p>‍</p><p>‍</p><p>‍</p></div><div class=\"margin-top margin-medium\"><div class=\"button-group\"><a data-theme=\"light\" data-btn-hover=\"\" href=\"mailto:workexperience@moonstone.co.ug\" class=\"btn w-inline-block\"><div class=\"btn__bg light\"></div><div class=\"btn__circle-wrap\"><div class=\"btn__circle light\"><div class=\"before__100\"></div></div></div><div class=\"btn__text light\"><p class=\"btn-text-p\">Apply </p></div></a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></header><div class=\"section_testimonial\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"divider-horizontal\"></div><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div fs-slider-type=\"cms\" fs-slider-instance=\"fs-1-card-slider\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_instance\"><div class=\"fs-1-card-slider_navigation-wrapper\"><div class=\"testimonial_icon-wrapper\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/assets/69010fb7542aa2ee07e42406_quote-2.svg\" alt=\"\" class=\"testimonial_icon\"></div></div><div class=\"fs-1-card-slider_list-wrapper\"><div class=\"fs-1-card-slider_list\"><div class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-xxlarge\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">A voice from within Moonstone...</div></div><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-xxlarge\"><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">From my very first day of work experience at Moonstone, colleagues took the time to involve me in meaningful matters and explain the ‘why’ behind the work. That inclusive, friendly, hands-on culture convinced me that Moonstone was where I wanted to build my legal career.</div></div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_logo-wrapper\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69ab00f29576db9e3341360c_resized_750x500_under_1MB_v2.avif\" alt=\"Young woman with bangs and a ponytail wearing a black sweater and necklace against a blue background.\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" srcset=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69ab00f29576db9e3341360c_resized_750x500_under_1MB_v2-p-500.avif 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69ab00f29576db9e3341360c_resized_750x500_under_1MB_v2.avif 750w\" class=\"testimonial_logo\"></div><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Daisy Jackman</div><div>Solicitor, Corporate &amp; Commercial</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>"},{"tag":"section","attrs":{"lottie":"trigger-scroll","className":"section_newsletter text-color-white"},"html":"<div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"wrapper_wide-screen\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"cta17_component\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid cta17_content\"><div class=\"newsletter_content-left\"><h2 data-scroll-speed=\"0.025\" data-scroll=\"\" class=\"heading-style-h3\">Stay informed. <br>Stay empowered.</h2><p data-scroll-speed=\"0.025\" data-scroll=\"\" class=\"text-size-medium\">Get practical advice, legal insights and firm updates, curated for you.</p></div><div class=\"cta17_content-right\"><div class=\"newsletter_form-block w-form\"><form id=\"wf-form-Newsletter-Sign-Up\" name=\"wf-form-Newsletter-Sign-Up\" data-name=\"Newsletter Sign Up\" method=\"get\" class=\"newsletter_form\" data-wf-page-id=\"695e4b79e26b3a377624a43c\" data-wf-element-id=\"a1c8c224-b7fc-d377-9351-7b7ff072db0a\"><div class=\"signup-form-wrapper\"><input class=\"form_input w-input\" maxlength=\"256\" name=\"Email\" data-name=\"Email\" placeholder=\"Enter your email\" type=\"email\" id=\"email\" required=\"\"><div class=\"form_icon-wrapper\"><div class=\"icon-embed-xsmall is-form w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 -960 960 960\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M676.2-445.93H188.09q-14.68 0-24.37-9.7-9.7-9.7-9.7-24.37 0-14.67 9.7-24.37 9.69-9.7 24.37-9.7H676.2L456.13-734.13q-10.2-10.2-10.33-24.0